{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1022871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "怎么设计算法才能做到既能得到1+1的结果，又能保证让大家不知道1+1=2呢", "timestamp": 1612033664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022875, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 无语。添加代价机制，当你屏蔽一个人的时候，随机抽取10个人，每人都有10%的几率被你屏蔽，次日重新抽取10人，直至你在某日取消屏蔽为止，作为你的屏蔽代价。", "timestamp": 1612034335, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022876, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 这不叫做屏蔽某个人发的树洞", "timestamp": 1612034445, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022877, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 感觉这个可以一起讨论，你上来没搞清楚情况就这样属实不行。", "timestamp": 1612034471, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022880, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我也只是随便瞎说一下，毕竟把时间线拉长，你的确只是屏蔽了一个人。", "timestamp": 1612034533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022882, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自己设计去，谁有空理你呀靠", "timestamp": 1612034732, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022884, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 而且你这个1+1如果换成一个比较复杂的问题，似乎就是经典的零知识证明的问题，既让大家知道你得出来正确结果，又不公布正确结果。不过你显然只是杠一下，而不是在说这件事。", "timestamp": 1612034829, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 行，给各位爷道歉了。", "timestamp": 1612034851, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022886, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 其实我想的和dz差不多。感觉叫有损屏蔽好一点。比如每k个人绑定在一起，屏蔽的时候自动屏蔽另外k-1个人。这样就一定程度能保护隐私吧大概", "timestamp": 1612035193, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我咋觉得你跟Alice在说同一件事。", "timestamp": 1612037937, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022896, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 可以这样：其它k个人可以每次随机挑选，并且被屏蔽的主要目标也不能设置为彻底屏蔽，因此需要主要目标的被屏蔽几率小于1但比其他人更接近1？", "timestamp": 1612038149, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022902, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我觉得洞主这个想法可行。换个角度 其实我们不是想屏蔽某个人，而是想屏蔽某种观点or价值取向。那就简单了，即除了参考标签外，我们对语义，文风等进行聚类分析，当我们屏蔽某条树洞时，更加相似的树洞将会有更大概率被屏蔽。当我们屏蔽的树洞明显与某些主题词相关时，树洞设计人员就可以把这个关键词也作为tag加上，方便我们进行有效屏蔽。", "timestamp": 1612039909, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022905, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 这和dz说的还有关系么。。", "timestamp": 1612041853, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1022994, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "很遗憾 要想达到「屏蔽某类观点」这个要求，凭借人类目前的NLP技术也只是能勉强做到，效果并不好。", "timestamp": 1612054473, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1023073, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "问题的后半句没看明白，假如有a,b,c三个人，现在要屏蔽c，需求是啥", "timestamp": 1612056560, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1023313, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你这和零知识证明不太一样啊", "timestamp": 1612060891, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1023381, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "..", "timestamp": 1612062103, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1023390, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有办法，屏蔽所有树洞", "timestamp": 1612062364, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1023444, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 203345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还聚类分析，你们出钱买服务器算力吗", "timestamp": 1612064046, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 203345, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "#203309\n怎么设计算法才能做到既能屏蔽某个人发的树洞，又能保证让大家不知道某个人发的所有树洞呢", "timestamp": 1612033593, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1612064048, "url": "", "vote": {}}}